Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:05.69,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:08.69,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting Chihaya in the \Nnumber three position.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:09.32,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.62,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,In the regional final,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.70,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hokuo went with even \Nmatch-ups across the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:17.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Do we really want to \Ndodge our opponents?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.33,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, you just have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:22.34,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Bring home the win!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.37,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Victory for Mizusawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:25.44,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:32.97,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:38.00,list2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1)}1. Yuube (Third-year) Class A\N2. Hayasaka (Second-year) Class B\N3. Ousaka (Third-year) Class A\N4. Nanase (Third-year) Class B\N5. Tanimura (Third-year) Class B
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.43,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi Girls might \Nchange up their order.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:38.76,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mention this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:41.10,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mention this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:42.39,Chiha-internal,Both,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:46.81,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,They probably went with the \Nsame order every match
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:50.98,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,as preparation for the strong \Nteams they'll face from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:54.03,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,They'll switch it up once they \Nface a strong team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:58.57,Chiha-internal,Both,0000,0000,0000,,So the question is whether Akashi \Nthinks we're good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:01.52,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,I will begin reading the order for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:04.31,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa High School versus \NFirst Akashi Girls' High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:07.00,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa High School, Nishida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:09.75,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,First Akashi Girls', Yuube-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.75,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Good, all according to plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.03,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa High School, Oe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:17.13,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,First Akashi Girls', Hayasaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:18.59,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,All according to plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.99,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa High School, Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:24.02,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,First Akashi Girls', Ousaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:25.64,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,All according to plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:28.10,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa High School, Mashima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.93,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,First Akashi Girls', Nanase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:34.41,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa High School, Komano-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:37.37,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,First Akashi Girls', Tanimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:40.12,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,It's so exactly according to our plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:41.70,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,it's kind of sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:44.96,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Are they looking ahead to the finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:47.21,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,They don't respect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.43,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:03.68,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,they have absolute faith \Nthat their ace will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:16.07,Chiha-title2,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1800)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:18.91,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}The \Nonly \Nsign \Nof \Nsummer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:19.01,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}Verse 12
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.57,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Megumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.82,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We're not playing Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.82,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:42.99,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:46.12,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.08,swoon,All,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Swoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:52.29,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is still the semifinal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.67,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu, how could you screw that up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.18,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,after they read the order?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.71,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,What?  But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.71,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,They should just let us play the final now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.39,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,Swoon!  Swoon!  Swoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:11.18,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,She really is ordinary and \Nsharp-tongued, yet popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:16.19,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-tan is our bitter and sweet idol...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.11,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,We first met her early last summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:23.53,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,during the brilliant First \NAkashi Girls' cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.03,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we're going to cut \Nto your flashback now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.66,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,We belong to the photography club \Nat the neighboring boys' school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.00,Chiha-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?  Taking pictures \Nwithout permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.88,Chiha-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.96,Chiha-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, there are perverts here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.76,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,Our intentions were pure,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.51,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,yet they called us perverts \Nfor taking a few pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.60,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,That was when...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.89,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:58.02,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to take pictures of \Nthe demonstration our club's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.07,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the competitive karuta club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.99,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-tan was so kind \Nand lovely that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:14.83,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.12,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,How did the pictures turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.21,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:17.88,Chiha-flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.34,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.21,delete,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Delete all pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.34,delete,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Deleting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:25.30,delete,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,No data
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.47,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to come take more pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.26,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll delete them when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:33.33,swoon,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,2002)}Swoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:40.48,Chiha-internal,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since, we've been taking \Npictures for Megumu-tan to delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.73,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.95,Chiha-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.91,Chiha-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,That picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.41,Chiha-main,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Megumu-tan's \Ntournament last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.16,Chiha-main,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to salvage it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.58,Chiha-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.15,Chiha-main,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,You've betrayed Megumu-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.09,Chiha-main,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,We can't allow the chronicle of \NMegumu-tan, the next Queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.84,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to be completely erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:09.34,Chiha-main,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, haven't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.72,Chiha-main,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-tan has changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.73,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Ousaka Megumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:25.57,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:28.61,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,If she was the West representative, \Nshe must be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.39,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,She lost to a veteran in \Nthe challenger final,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:35.33,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,but she may be the one who \Nfaces Wakamiya Shinobu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.61,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Queen match this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.62,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.08,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:38.66,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one in glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.67,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.83,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,There.  The one putting on a headband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.96,Chiha-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,She must be fast, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.71,Chiha-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she'll lose to \Nanyone in her age group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.21,Chiha-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like she's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.80,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but her opponent's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.25,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,When I watched Ousaka-san last fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:01.48,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,she was more focused on adapting \Nto her opponent than being fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.57,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be careful and accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.57,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody helped to give me this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:16.54,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:20.16,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I worked, \NI couldn't have made it here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.46,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.88,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Omi Jingu tatami is for five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:35.31,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,They should just let \Nus play the final now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.56,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.10,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,We will begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.86,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.23,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:57.91,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:07.25,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:04.19,ionno3,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,126)}Creepy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:17.64,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, \Nnow the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:26.23,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of birds crossing \Nfrom Awaji Island
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:30.15,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-tan is faster now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.91,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,She's way faster now than when she was in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.12,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,last year's Queen match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:41.66,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.91,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one card at a time, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:44.67,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.22,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi Girls' has this match in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.30,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa placed second \Nin the Tokyo regional,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.47,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and Group B didn't have \Nany strong opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:02.47,Chiha-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi Girls has them beat in \Nboth history and current lineup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.19,Chiha-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,The match to watch is definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:08.31,ionno,C,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}Creepy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.73,Chiha-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,Hokuo against Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.86,Chiha-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,The real final.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:19.95,Chiha-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya-kun, what was \Nyour objective today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.58,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.37,Chiha-flashback,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to cheer for \Nmy friends from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.17,Chiha-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're no longer \Nallowed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.30,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,So he's cheering for Hokuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.21,ionno2,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,200)}Creepy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:41.22,Chiha-internal,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, Mizusawa prevented us \Nfrom making it to Nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:45.60,Chiha-internal,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,Amakasu and Takuma are the only \Nones with experience at Nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.52,Chiha-internal,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,This year, we were able to bring \Nsome first and second-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.32,Chiha-internal,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,Fujisaki is fielding five third-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.23,Chiha-internal,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,If we beat them here, they \Nwon't be a threat next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.74,Chiha-internal,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,You can do this, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.74,Chiha-internal,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:03.79,coach,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Fujisaki High School\NKaruta Advisor\N Sakurazawa Midori (39)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:02.66,Chiha-internal,Mochi,0000,0000,0000,,...really scared of Coach \NSakurazawa from Fujisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:09.04,Chiha-main,Saku,0000,0000,0000,,The players from Akashi Girls' \Nare playing well, Coach Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.29,Chiha-main,Saku,0000,0000,0000,,Ousaka-san is a strong weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.25,Chiha-main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, Coach Sakurazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:19.29,coach,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}{\an3}First Akashi Girls' \NKaruta Advisor\N Minami Daigoro
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.80,Chiha-main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's in a groove!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.09,Chiha-main,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to an exciting final,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.30,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,whether it's against Hokuo or Fujisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.31,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:28.69,Chiha-main,Saku,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.56,Chiha-main,Rion,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:39.15,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,When I watched Ousaka-san last \Nfall, she didn't seem that fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.49,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but she attacked that \Ncard at full speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.02,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Being too aggressive with \N"The sound of birds" is risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:47.04,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Was she camping that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.54,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,when I should have \Ngone to sleep instead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:52.63,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She passed me the only \N"A" card on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.61,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be targeting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:57.88,Chiha-main,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:10:59.93,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:00.03,alumni2,,0000,0000,0000,,Older alumni
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.20,alumni2,,0000,0000,0000,,Older alumni
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.47,alumni,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Older alumni
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.47,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I holding this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:12.31,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,awakens the guards of \NSuma Gate at night
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:19.32,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}While the autumn leaves of \NMount Ogura would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:16.82,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,Tough luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.11,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,She shielded the "While autumn" on her right,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.24,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,but "While the autumn" was read instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.70,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't have done \Nanything about that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.28,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.24,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's still early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.04,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I need my first card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.41,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,One card at a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:30.00,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.08,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,people would always ask if \NI was pining for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.00,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The only "Since" card on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:41.84,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, she plays a tougher game \Nthan her appearance lets on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.60,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,"A night" and "Since I"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.72,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,are cards that Ayase likes to \Nattack on the opponent's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:51.27,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they're on her side, she'll\Nfeel like she has to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:52.77,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.48,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,One card at a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.28,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,She'll feel like she's on the defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.90,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The opposing team is made \Nup of slender girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.29,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,yet they look so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.39,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,They're moving in tandem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.54,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:19.80,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Are the headbands the key?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.83,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I should make headbands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:28.03,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother can easily win if he tries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.58,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsukuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:30.79,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,How can you fall asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:31.60,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.86,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,But I played three matches in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:36.51,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,No ifs or buts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:39.11,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't understand how tough it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:44.36,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking three to four \Nserious matches in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.98,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man and I'm about ready \Nto fall asleep on my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:50.11,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oe-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.67,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,This being her fourth match today,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:55.47,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe-senpai is the one most likely \Nto be running low on stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.71,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since she lost her second
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:01.13,2cards1,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)\an4}Lost by 2 cards
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:01.13,2cards2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)}Lost by 2 cards
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.63,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and third games by 2 cards each...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.13,lotcards,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)}Lost by a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:06.72,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,It really hurts when you fight hard, \Nonly to lose at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.89,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna lose \Nanyway, you might as well
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.76,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,let yourself be blown out \Nso you can get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.55,blown,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Blown out of \Nall his games
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.81,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oe-senpai isn't the only \None I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:20.71,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Komano-senpai's first game \Ntoday comes in the semifinal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.93,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-senpai is up against \Nthe opponent's ace
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:24.99,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and just lost two cards in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.79,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's usually up to the \Nace to set the tone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:37.95,cell2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)}Outbox \NTo: Mom \NRe: Nationals \NYour brother the ace has \Nled the team to the \Nsemifinals! \N The championship is \Nwithin sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:35.32,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,"Your brother the ace has led \Nthe team to the semifinals!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.83,bro,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}That's our Bro            So cool
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.17,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,"The championship is within sight!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:41.46,cell2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\fad(400,400)}Inbox\N From: Mom\N Re: Re: Nationals\N That's our Bro!  \NGood luck! \N Take a picture \Nwhen you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:44.53,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I can always say that \NI jammed my finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:48.79,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Do I attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:50.59,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Defend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:52.71,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't doubt myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:54.52,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't doubt myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:56.41,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't doubt myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:00.80,Chiha-flashback,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, when in \Ntrouble, go lower right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.82,Chiha-flashback,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Always go to the lower right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.82,Chiha-flashback,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you check their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:07.94,Chiha-flashback,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,In Ousaka Megumu's case,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:10.52,Chiha-flashback,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,she's probably good at "While it pains," \N"While it may," "While it brings," and "Long,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:11.83,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,the cards with the starting sounds of her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:14.20,Me,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1)}Me (Long)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.21,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Her best card is at her lower right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:25.71,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,I beseech them to wait for the \NEmperor's return before falling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:33.27,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Long last we meet, only for \Nme to leave hurriedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.39,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,She knew to pay extra attention \Nto "Long last we meet"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.08,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.27,Chiha-internal,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,No need to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.65,Chiha-internal,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-senpai would never lose "Long."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:52.24,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My opponent's card in the lower right was \Nread right when I set my eye on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:56.47,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the West representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.00,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:04.71,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's much faster than she was that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.21,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She has the potential to become Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:08.22,Chiha-main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.88,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.35,Chiha-main,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,You got mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.46,Chiha-main,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you holding \Nthree of the same card?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:16.27,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:17.89,swoon,All,0000,0000,0000,,Swoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.64,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one more card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:22.40,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:33.16,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,There's a saying that \Nboys grow up very fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:35.34,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,but the same applies to girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.99,Chiha-flashback,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,You should all get \Nserious about karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:41.02,Chiha-flashback,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,The Kyoto tournament is in May!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.54,Chiha-flashback,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Any application fees will \Nbe paid by the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:45.87,Chiha-flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pain, Daigoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.40,Chiha-flashback,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,Use your energy on the volleyball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.22,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,The karuta club had plenty of history,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.19,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,but it wasn't particularly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:57.14,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Ousaka practiced all the \Ntime at her karuta society,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.05,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,but she never tried very \Nhard during club practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:02.63,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Everything changed after the Queen \Nchallenger final in October.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.74,Chiha-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,The West representative \Nis Ousaka Megumu from
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.32,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,the Akashi Karuta Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:16.35,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,She'd always had the talent,\N but this time she was also lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.48,Chiha-internal,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Megumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:19.86,Chiha-internal,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is the challenger final?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:21.58,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If you win that, you get to play the Queen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.80,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Her classmates and friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.13,GLM,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Megumu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:29.73,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,...believed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.55,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,...she could become Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:45.35,Chiha-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad for Ousaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.30,Chiha-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,She made it this far \Non beginner's luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.36,Chiha-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not enough \Nto face the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:54.81,Chiha-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto Yumi-san had more \Ndedication and motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.62,Chiha-flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu, are you upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:03.68,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:06.21,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely wasn't as good as she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:09.69,Chiha-flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:10.63,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:15.38,Chiha-flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help, so let's practice until you're \Ninvested enough to get upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.24,Chiha-flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make you Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:25.39,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is working together to \Nmake Ousaka Megumu the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.43,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,I tear up when I think
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.24,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,of how hard they've \Nbeen working ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.40,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm a grown man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.73,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,She got used to all the attention
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:41.65,banner65,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Ignoring...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:40.55,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,she draws as the last West Representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:46.14,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,This proves that circumstances \Ncan change a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.80,Chiha-flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The ace usually plays \Nin the third position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:52.17,Chiha-flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll put Megumu in the \Nthird position every match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.04,Chiha-flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to get Megumu \Nmore experience, not win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:18:03.64,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,...like the moon hidden \Nbehind the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:11.44,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Said night was young when \Nthe false rooster's crow,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.80,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't marked that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:11.83,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.11,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's taken four cards in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.57,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I need my first card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:15.94,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My first card...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.45,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,banish any lingering memories of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:28.90,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,but the gates of Afusaka remained shut
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:36.07,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,When winds blow oak leaves in the twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:32.85,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.07,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:37.71,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:38.76,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:40.73,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:42.90,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:44.91,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:56.93,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,"When winds blow," Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.01,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:20.50,Chiha-poem,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,When winds blow oak \Nleaves in the twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.74,Chiha-poem,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,the only sign of summer is the \Nritual purification in the waters
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:28.99,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:36.61,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,This poem by Junii Ietaka
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:42.05,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,describes a comfortable \Nlast day of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:50.01,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,This day will define our entire summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:58.43,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oe-senpai is leading by 4 cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:02.25,Chiha-internal,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably tired!  Exhausted, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:09.01,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,That card is more than \N"When wind blows"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:11.67,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,More than three syllables...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:19.19,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, when this poem \Nwas written 800 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.80,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,they must have felt very refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:37.60,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}the only sign of summer is the \Nritual purification in the waters
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:34.71,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,They could
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:38.65,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,probably hear the wind blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:44.78,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Silent waves creep closer to the \NSuminoe shore, and when night falls,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:45.64,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:47.93,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.01,Chiha-internal,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.71,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:55.83,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.65,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of dreams, \Nthere's "Silent waves"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:05.05,Chiha-card-TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1317,1)}in my dreams, I creep closer to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:14.69,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:16.90,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.68,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,have a good match!
